CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Cyclo Therapeutics Inc is a clinical-stage biotechnology firm. The company develops cyclodextrin-based products for the treatment of disease. Its lead drug candidate, Trappsol Cyclo, treats Niemann-Pick Type C disease (NPC). Its other products include Trappsol HPB, Trappsol Fine Chemical, and Aquaplex.
